 by the Einstein equation\nwith a negative cosmological constant. Therefore, the Einstein equation can be\nregarded as the equation of original quantum state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Aug 2014 10:32:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Aug 2014 15:44:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2015 13:06:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-04"}
